<http://www.example.org/eudamed> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "Abel Florensa Palau" .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> "2026-04-12" .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "An ontology modelling the European catalogue of high-risk medical devices and in-vitro diagnostics under MDR (EU 2017/745) and IVDR (EU 2017/746) regulations." .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "EUDAMED Medical Devices Ontology" .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "1.0.0" .
