# http://www.example.org/eudamed#hasIdentifiedRisk
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#hasIdentifiedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#hasIdentifiedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/eudamed#MedicalDevice> .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#hasIdentifiedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.example.org/eudamed#Risk> .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#hasIdentifiedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates a medical device to a risk identified for that device type." .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#hasIdentifiedRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has identified risk" .
# 
# http://www.example.org/eudamed#hasRiskClass
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#hasRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#hasRiskClass> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.example.org/eudamed#MedicalDevice> .
