<http://www.example.org/eudamed#involvesRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.example.org/eudamed#Risk> .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#involvesRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates an incident to the risk that materialised." .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#involvesRisk> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "involves risk" .
# 
# http://www.example.org/eudamed#isManufacturedBy
