<http://www.example.org/eudamed#isReportedFor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates an incident to the medical device involved in the event." .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#isReportedFor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is reported for" .
# 
# http://www.example.org/eudamed#isSubclassifiedUnder
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#isSubclassifiedUnder> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
