<http://www.example.org/eudamed#isSubclassifiedUnder> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.example.org/eudamed#RegulatoryClass> .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#isSubclassifiedUnder> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Transitive property relating a risk class to a higher risk class in the regulatory hierarchy." .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#isSubclassifiedUnder> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is subclassified under" .
# 
# http://www.example.org/eudamed#triggersCorrectiveAction
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#triggersCorrectiveAction> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
