<http://www.example.org/eudamed#triggersCorrectiveAction> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates an incident to the field safety corrective action it prompted." .
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#triggersCorrectiveAction> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "triggers corrective action" .
