<http://www.example.org/eudamed#isImplantable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is implantable" .
# 
# http://www.example.org/eudamed#isReusable
<http://www.example.org/eudamed#isReusable> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
